&lt;a href="#%ea%b8%b0%ec%88%a0-%ea%b2%80%ed%86%a0-%ed%94%84%eb%a1%9c%ec%84%b8%ec%8a%a4" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>준비 단계&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>검토 범위 정의&lt;/li>
&lt;li>참여자 선정&lt;/li>
